          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The  total  photoneutron  cross section  of Pb-208 was",
                " measured between    8    and   13   MeV   using   the",
                " bremsstrahlung photon facility  from  35  MeV  linac.",
                " Considerable resonance  structure was observed in the",
                " cross section,  of which the peak around  9  MeV,  as",
                " well as  the  structure around 10.8 mev may be due to",
                " E2 excitations."
              ]
            }
